say “don’t do this, don’t do that."

17
00:01:54,180 --> 00:02:01,200
I never say that, it just happens,
because when the virtue starts developing,

18
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:05,692
the vibrations improve and
you feel extremely joyous.

19
00:02:06,420 --> 00:02:16,440
We have lost our virtues because
there is no joy out of it, no reward.

20
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:19,139
If somebody is honest, he has to suffer;

21
00:02:19,380 --> 00:02:24,600
