not, just given her two rooms.

29
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:49,740
It’s not good!”

30
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:51,480
I said, “Let it be, doesn’t matter.

31
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:54,405
I know for nothing is going
to happen, let her be here."

32
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:56,580
So they wouldn’t also go against Me.

33
00:02:56,580 --> 00:02:57,840
They said, “All right, if you say so."

34
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:00,780
This lady stayed for ten days and went away.

35
00:03:00,780 --> 00:03:05,700
Then she become a very well-known actress in
India, I didn’t know she was the same lady,

36
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:07,560
but somebody told Me that she is the same lady.

37
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:09,069
I said, “Maybe."

38
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:13,485
Then one day you see, they wanted
to make a film for our Sahaja Yoga,

39
00:03:13,620 --> 00:03:17,760
so they said, “We can ask this lady to
act, because she is a good actress."

40
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:22,860
I said, “All right, you can go ask but don’t tell
her I am here, otherwise she will have no choice.

41
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:24,420
I will not go and see her.

42
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:25,740
You just ask her."

43
00:03:25,740 --> 00:03:28,860
They went and ask her, they said,
“Will you be actress?” and all that.

44
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:29,940
She said, “I’ll try."

45
00:03:29,940 --> 00:03:31,140
This, that she was saying.

46
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:36,060
But on the day on when they were going to open the
film I went there, she saw Me, she was so amazed,

47
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:40,800
she said, “Oh God, You are the One, You
are the One Who is sponsoring this, Oh,

48
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:44,460
I’ll give my life for Her!” She just came
forward, she said, “Have anything you like,

49
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:49,692
I have nothing to say, I am so sorry
that you never told me that She’s there."

50
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:54,563
Thousand times more she rewarded
a little thing I did for her.

51
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,840
No more cheating, no more troubling,

52
