the world for you, you will be amazed.

55
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:17,700
It’s such a tremendous thing happens,
because now you all are awakened in

56
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:20,760
that Primordial Being and you
have become one with each other.

57
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:27,960
You can feel it, that oneness, that unison that
