68
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:18,600
Word comes from “religo,” in Sanskrit it means
dharma, “Dhariyatisa Dharma,” the sustenance,

69
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,700
your sustenance, your valances is your religion.

70
00:05:20,700 --> 00:05:26,580
As every atom, carbon has four valances,
